data.description: Don't Miss Out on this Ranch Style 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom, 2 car Garage Home in The Outlook Village neighborhood. Open entryway ready leading into vaulted ceiling Living Room with gas fireplace and beautiful crown modeling. Once in the Living Room you have a cut-out Bar into the Kitchen that leads to an Eat-in-Kitchen Dinning area with bay windows looking out onto the front yard and Park across the street. In the Kitchen you have Corian countertops and tons of cabinet storage. Down the hallway you have 2 larger guest Bedrooms, sharing 1 Full Bathroom. The Laundry Room is conveniently located on the main level as well. On the other side of the hall you have a beautiful Primary Master Bedroom with vaulted ceilings and plentifully sun lit from the large east facing windows. The En-Suite Five Piece Master Bath features a large walk-in closet. Downstairs is a wide open unfinished Basement where the possibilities are endless. Out the Backdoor you have a cozy patio and a huge raised gardening bed, in addition to a small yard. BBQ's and garden party ready! Across the street is a beautiful Park with a playground in this very quiet and charming neighborhood. Location is great to all school ages, restaurants, shopping, golf courses and major highways. Book a showing today!
